  "_aboutBody": {
    "value": "For over three decades, Duran's Station has been a cornerstone of Albuquerque's culinary scene, renowned for preserving and perfecting traditional New Mexican cuisine. Our commitment to using locally sourced chiles and time-honored family recipes ensures an authentic taste experience you won't find anywhere else. We invite you to become part of our family tradition, where every meal is a celebration of our heritage.",
